data.meta_description: The 25th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival is a three-day event held Feb. 17-19, 2023 at the Sarasota Fairgrounds to benefit Suncoast Charities for Children.  Bring your lawn chair
data.text: The 25th Annual Thunder By The Bay Music & Motorcycle Festival is a three-day event held Feb. 17-19, 2023 at the Sarasota Fairgrounds to benefit Suncoast Charities for Children. Bring your lawn chair and enjoy continuous live music. Featured headline acts include 38 Special (Saturday - February 18) and Colt Ford (Sunday – February 19). The Festival features over 100 vendors, motorcycle freestyle shows, a charity motorcycle ride, 17 class bike show, a motorcycle stereo contest, a burnout contest, a “little riders” kid zone, great food, a “Born To Be Wild” Festival kickoff party, and much more! Dry & full-service camping is available on-site. Admission is $10 in advance and $15 at the gate (12 and under free). Limited VIP tickets are also available. For more information visit: thunderbythebay.org
